#: ../DISCOVER/09_participant_selection.md:88
msgid ""
"‚úÖ Regardless of which approach you choose, open or anonymized, we "
"encourage you to make it &quot;double&quot; so that both parties know "
"each other (double-open) or neither party knows the other (double-closed)"
